  "comment": "Battery-Operated 6 x 12W RGBWAUV LED PAR: Lightweight and compact, EVENTPAR battery-operated PARs are the best wireless solutions for all your parties and events. Extremely easy to use for installation flexibility far exceeding traditional wired systems, this projector is designed to create a wide range of customisable atmospheres thanks to its 6 powerful RGBWA+UV LEDs of 12 watts each capable of reproducing the most common colours, but also amber and UV with a beam angle of 25° for even more powerful and varied colour effects. Controllable by DMX and incorporating wireless DMX technology, the EVENTPARs can be easily positioned and operated remotely. With 20 hours of autonomy in single-colour mode, they are an indispensable accessory for decorating large or small spaces. The EVENT-PAR-FC charging station (available as an option) allows you to charge up to 6 EVENTPARs in a single flight case to rapidly deploy the solution during your performances.",
